  "description": "A high-density scalp electroencephalogram (EEG) dataset acquired during sensorimotor rhythm-based brain-computer interface (BCI) tasks. This dataset comprises recordings from subjects performing motor imagery and sensorimotor rhythm modulation tasks, designed to support the development and validation of BCI systems. The dataset is intended to facilitate research in neural signal processing, motor control, and brain-computer interface applications.",
